                        <h1 class="u-mb-l u-fs-xxl">Private or rented accommodation</h1>

                        <div class="page__body">
                            <p>It’s the householder’s responsibility to complete the census.</p>
                            
                            <p>The householder is a person who usually lives at this address, and on their own or with someone else:</p>
                            
                            {{
                                onsList({
                                    "itemsList": [
                                        {
                                            "text": "owns or rents the accommodation, or"
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "text": "pays the household bills and expenses"
                                        }
                                    ]
                                })
                            }}
                            
                            <p>Still not sure? The following advice will help you understand who should complete the form.</p>
                            
                            <h2>If the landlord lives here</h2>
                            
                            <p>The landlord and tenants who pay bills are all householders. One of you will need to complete the accommodation questions, but each tenant can complete their own individual questions.</p>
                            
                            <h2>If you live here but your landlord doesn’t</h2>
                            
                            <p>The tenant or tenants who pay the bills for the household should complete the form. This could be you, someone else, or everyone who lives here.</p>
                            
                            <p>One person will need to take responsibility for answering the questions about the home, but each tenant can complete their own individual questions.</p>
                            
                            <div id="details" class="collapsible js-collapsible u-mb-m collapsible--initialised" data-btn-close="Hide this" role="group">
                                <div class="collapsible__heading js-collapsible-heading" role="link" aria-controls="details" tabindex="0" aria-expanded="false" data-ga-action="Close panel"><div class="collapsible__controls">
